public FormatException(java.lang.String message)
Constructs a new format exception with the specified detail message. The cause is not initialized, and may subsequently be initialized by a call to Throwable.initCause(java.lang.Throwable).

message - the detail message. The detail message is saved for later retrieval by the Throwable.getMessage() method.
